{
  "id": "adv_event_2205_01_03",
  "title": "後悔なんて、\nしたくない",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 0.9999999881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3……ここで……っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2‚ 3… Here…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2,
      "endTime": 5.1333333332999995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "ひゃっ？　お、お姉ちゃん？\nどうして急に一歩引いたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hya? O-onee-chan?\nWhy did you suddenly step back?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.1666666667,
      "endTime": 10.133333237999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "ここはブレイクが入るでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is where the break comes in‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3666666667,
      "endTime": 12.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ここで千紗が前に出て私が真後ろに立てば\n千紗がもっと目立てるかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Chisa steps forward here and I stand right behind‚\nChisa will stand out more‚ I thought.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.0666666667,
      "endTime": 19.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも、そしたら……お姉ちゃんの動きだけとっても\n大げさになるよ？　不自然じゃないかな……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ um‚ then… your movements alone will become\nexaggerated. Won't it look unnatural?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.8,
      "endTime": 29.2999999129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫、心配しないで\n……これでいいのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's fine‚ don't worry.\n…This is how it should be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.5,
      "endTime": 35.1425848007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Onee-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.9,
      "endTime": 36.8366440058,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ、今日の練習はこれくらいにしておこうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew‚ let's end today's practice here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.9333333333,
      "endTime": 44.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "うん……お疲れ様",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… Good work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2,
      "endTime": 46.933333333300006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "あら？　{user}さんが呼んでる……\n私を呼んでるみたい。ちょっと行ってくるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? {user}-san is calling…\nIt seems like he is calling me. I'll go for a moment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.0666666667,
      "endTime": 55.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7899.999999999998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん……練習の間\nずっと私を目立たせようとばかりしてた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Onee-chan… during practice\nshe was always trying to make me stand out…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.0666666667,
      "endTime": 62.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか、大会が始まる前より酷くなってる気がする\n言った方がいいのかな？　でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels like it's getting worse before the competition starts.\nShould I say something? But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.3333333333,
      "endTime": 72.53333333329999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんは何も言わないし……\n聞いちゃいけないかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Onee-chan doesn't say anything…\nShould I ask…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.8333333333,
      "endTime": 77.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "このままじゃきっとダメなのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we continue like this‚ it won't work…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.0333333333,
      "endTime": 81.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "どうして私は、肝心な時にお姉ちゃんの力に\nなれないんだろ……情けないな、私……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why can't I become a support for Onee-chan\nat crucial times… I'm pathetic…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.8666666667,
      "endTime": 90.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7333333333,
      "endTime": 94.46789112879999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん、どうしたの？\nもしかして、お皿洗いがイヤになったとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa-chan‚ what's wrong?\nDid you get tired of washing dishes?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6666666667,
      "endTime": 100.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "う、ううん、違うよ、ごめんね？\nその……あ、いや、やっぱり、なんでもない、よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no‚ it's not that. Sorry.\nUm… well‚ it's nothing‚ really.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.5,
      "endTime": 110.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかして、沙季ちゃんとのユニットで悩んでる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Could it be that you're worried about the team with Saki-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.7333333333,
      "endTime": 117.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "へっ！？　え、あ、な、なんで分かるの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!? E-eh‚ why did you know…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.4,
      "endTime": 121.16666666670001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "だって最近、千紗ちゃんも沙季ちゃんもずっと\n悩んだ顔してるんだもん。みんなも心配してるよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because lately‚ both Chisa-chan and Saki-chan\nhave been wearing troubled expressions. Everyone is worried‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.3333333333,
      "endTime": 128.6297995075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "わ、わわ、みんなに心配させちゃってたんだ……\nご、ごめんなさい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I've been worrying everyone…?\nI-I'm sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.8333333333,
      "endTime": 135.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "気にしなくていいよ。みんなで支え合ってこそでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry about it. We support each other‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.0666666667,
      "endTime": 140.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "ね、悩み……聞かせてもらってもいい？\n力になれるかは分からないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ can I listen to your worries?\nI don't know if I can help‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5333333333,
      "endTime": 148.34528334930002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "……う、うん、その……聞いてくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Y-yeah‚ um… can you listen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.8,
      "endTime": 153.37274370190002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんだよ。でもその前に……\n残りのお皿洗いを頑張って終わらせないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. But before that…\nWe should finish washing the rest of the dishes‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.5666666667,
      "endTime": 161.15126978549998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "う、うんっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yeah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.5333333333,
      "endTime": 162.99999999989998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "そっか、千紗ちゃんも沙季ちゃんも\nお互い譲り合っちゃってるんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ both Chisa-chan and Saki-chan\nhave been accommodating each other.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.1666666667,
      "endTime": 170.6910428682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "な、渚ちゃんから見て、私とお姉ちゃんのユニットは\nどう見えてたかな……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ how did you see me and Onee-chan's team?\nWhat did it look like to you‚ Nagisa-chan…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.1333333333,
      "endTime": 177.4333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
