      "text": "とっても素敵だと思うよ\nでも……千紗ちゃんが言ってることも分かる、かな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it's really wonderful.\nBut… I can understand what you're saying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.7333333333,
      "endTime": 186.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか、千紗ちゃんも沙季ちゃんも\nちょっと苦しそうだな……って思ってたんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like both Chisa-chan and Saki-chan\nare struggling a bit… that's what I thought.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.3333333333,
      "endTime": 193.29999999999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "苦しそう……そっか、やっぱり\n見てる人にも伝わってるんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Struggling… I see‚ so\nit's visible to others too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.5333333333,
      "endTime": 201.0557821592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
