      "text": "う、うん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ okay…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 360.3,
      "endTime": 362.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs032.m4a",
      "text": "（今、無理やりでも本音を言えば良かった……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I should've spoken my true feelings‚ even if it was forced…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 363.0333333333,
      "endTime": 367.2780044873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs033.m4a",
      "text": "（せっかく勇気をもらったのに……）\n（ごめんね？　渚ちゃん……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I had gained courage‚ but…)\n(Sorry… Nagisa-chan…)",
