        "en": "We managed to win the semifinals somehow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 375.5666666667,
      "endTime": 378.9978231112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs034.m4a",
      "text": "うん、ほんとに良かった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I'm really glad…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 379.2,
      "endTime": 381.7351248264,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "それで、次の決勝なんだけど……\n私に考えがあるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ onto the finals…\nI have an idea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 382.1333333333,
      "endTime": 389.0388208707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs035.m4a",
      "text": "へ？　何か作戦があるの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Do you have a plan…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 389.1666666667,
      "endTime": 392.1991610209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、このユニットは徹底的に千紗を立てたいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I still want to prioritize Chisa in our team.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 392.6666666667,
      "endTime": 397.6141724269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs036.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうして……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Why…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 397.8,
      "endTime": 399.856349206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "だって、今のままじゃ、お客さんもどちらを見たら\nいいか分からないでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because as it is now‚ the audience wouldn't know\nwho to focus on‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 400.1666666667,
      "endTime": 406.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_03-chs037.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも、二人組なんだし\nお姉ちゃんも私も、両方見てもらえれば……",
      "translations": {
